## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Requirements change mid-project | High | Use Agile for uncertain areas, Waterfall for stable core |
| Stakeholder unavailable for review | Medium | Schedule reviews in advance, use async review tools |
| Documentation falls behind code | High | Enforce DoD: no code merge without updated docs |
| Compliance audit failure | Critical | Run Phase 09 audit early and often |

