## Review & Approval Process

### Documentation Review Cadence

[For Waterfall:]
- **Requirements Review:** After Phase 02 complete (formal signoff)
- **Design Review:** After Phase 03 complete (architecture review board)
- **Final Review:** After Phase 09 complete (compliance audit)

[For Agile:]
- **Sprint Review:** Review docs updated during sprint (part of DoD)
- **Release Review:** Review all docs before major release
- **Quarterly Review:** Ensure docs are up-to-date

### Approval Workflow

1. **Author:** Generate documentation using SDLC-Docs-Engine skills
2. **Peer Review:** Technical review by team members
3. **Stakeholder Review:** Business/product owner review
4. **Approval:** Formal signoff by [role/name]
5. **Archive:** Version and store in [location]

